{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_04_end","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-4","storyName":"无人的小巷","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"城中，塞雷娅正要将动力甲彻底击溃，千钧一发之际，博士出声阻止，从动力甲中救出了缪尔赛思；城外，一行人终于进入多萝西的实验室，拓荒者们却第一时间将弓弩对准多萝西。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["Mechanist","塞雷娅","奇怪的动力甲","桑尼","拓荒队成员","白面鸮","埃琳娜","赫默","温柔的女声","格雷伊","？？？","玛丽","多萝西"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":7},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"黑色填满了整个狭小的空间，隔绝了光线、空气与声响。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":8},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"想用嘴呼喊。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"源石引擎运作带来的高温塞住了喉管，没有声音能发出来。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"想用手敲打。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"坚硬的钢铁紧紧压住了四肢，连躲闪的余地都没有，谈何反抗。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"要是能落下眼泪就好了。从小妈妈就说，泪水是很好的武器。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可是眼睛不愿意。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"数百年来，它们看过太多崩塌的山和干涸的水，也见证了太多亲人的消逝。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"800","id":15},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"它们变得越来越干燥，就像移动城市碾过的土地。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","id":17},{"type":"Dialog","id":18},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":21},{"type":"Character","id":22},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g8_alley_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":23},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$chasing_intro","key":"$chasing_loop","volume":"0.7","id":25,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"第六具动力甲，确认瘫痪。","id":29},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"这些就是全部？","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"看起来是这样。他们成功拖住了我们十三分钟。","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"等等——","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"扫描结果显示，还有第七具！","id":35},{"type":"dialog","id":36},{"type":"character","id":37},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mechawalk","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","fadetime":"2.5","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奇怪的动力甲","text":"——","id":41},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"Dialog","id":43},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mecharun","id":45},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"300","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":46},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士小心！它往你的方向去了！","id":50},{"type":"dialog","id":51},{"type":"character","id":52},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_empty","id":53},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":55},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"200","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":56},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.7","id":57},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奇怪的动力甲","text":"——","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":60},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"100","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"0.61","id":62},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","id":63},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":64},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":66},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0.51","block":"false","id":67},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":69},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.6","id":70},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":72},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"让我来。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_526_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1","id":75},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-60","fadetime":"0.51","block":"false","id":77},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.6","id":78},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"0.52","id":80},{"type":"Text","text":"你看不清塞雷娅是怎么移动的，在你的双腿反应过来之前，她已经站在了你的面前。","id":81},{"type":"Text","text":"你知道，在哥伦比亚的街道上，她从来不会带上那面莱茵制造的盾牌。","id":82},{"type":"Text","text":"她会把自己变成盾。","id":83},{"type":"Text","text":"从她交叠的小臂上，珐琅质迅速生长开，替你挡下了动力甲的一击。","id":84},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"害虫。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":87},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"1","id":88},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.4","id":89},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":90},{"type":"Text","text":"你听到塞雷娅低声说。","id":91},{"type":"Text","text":"她一直这么看待这些失控的哥伦比亚技术。","id":92},{"type":"Text","text":"从她的表情与姿态中，你读出了她下一步的动作。","id":93},{"type":"Text","text":"在准备消灭害虫的时候，塞雷娅从来不会浪费时间。","id":94},{"type":"Text","text":"她的手即将触到动力甲的前胸，那里很快就会出现一个黑黢黢的空洞——","id":95},{"type":"Text","text":"面前这具动力甲会被摧毁，或者说，“死去”。","id":96},{"type":"Text","text":"一个念头在你的脑子里蹿了上来。","id":97},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"MusicVolume","volume":"0.1","fadetime":"1","id":99},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"101","text":"停下，塞雷娅！"}],"values":[],"id":100},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":101,"end":103},{"type":"Text","text":"塞雷娅也许只听到了你喊出来的第一个音节，但她的确收了手。","id":102},{"type":"Text","text":"这是你们长期并肩作战累积下来的信任。","id":103,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":104},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_circleatk_h","text":"","id":105},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":106},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":109},{"type":"Text","text":"她的拳头错开了核心，可攻击的余波依旧震碎了动力甲的上半截外壳。","id":110},{"type":"Text","text":"从无数飞溅的金属碎片中，你看到了一抹亮色。","id":111},{"type":"Text","text":"就像......发丝。","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，危险！别靠近——","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#5$1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"那是......","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_532_1#5$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":117},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"Character","id":120},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.7","id":121,"musicid":1},{"type":"Image","image":"29_i02","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","fadetime":"0","id":122},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","duration":"40","block":"false","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":125},{"type":"Text","text":"动力甲正在倒下。","id":126},{"type":"Text","text":"更多碎片飞了出来，很快，你看到了更多发丝，一点皮肤，然后是一只眼睛。","id":127},{"type":"Text","text":"那只眼睛看向了你。","id":128},{"type":"Text","text":"愤怒，惊恐，迷茫......你在一瞬间读出了很多情绪。","id":129},{"type":"Text","text":"而在所有情绪随着伪装的外壳一起剥落之后，你发现它在向你求救。","id":130},{"type":"Text","text":"于是，你伸出了一只手。","id":131},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":134},{"type":"Character","id":135},{"type":"Image","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":137},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":138},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"140","text":"你好，缪尔赛思。"}],"values":[],"id":139},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":140,"end":200},{"type":"Dialog","id":141},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":144},{"type":"Character","id":145},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g4_corridor","screenadapt":"showall","id":146},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":147},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.7","id":148,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":150},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"迈尔，这是怎么回事？","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我不知道......我不知道，领队......","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你先放开摩尔医生。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"医生......","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......","id":160,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我不能放开她。","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你不听我的命令？","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"领队，你为什么还跟她们站在一起？","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"你不是说，我们必须狠下心来对她们下手吗？你不是说......我们只是她们豢养的实验动物吗？","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"是你劝我跟你一块干的。我本来......我很喜欢摩尔医生。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......没想到，最先站出来反对我的人会是你。","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我甚至想过会是萨姆，或者其他人......迈尔，你从来都最听我的话。","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"你也说过，我太听话了。","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"以前我听老板的，在工厂里得了矿石病......来了这里，我就听你的。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"你们都是有本事的人，聪明，读书多。我觉得听你们的不会错。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"但现在......我们都要死了。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"桑尼，我们都快被这几个做研究的人害死了！她们还觉得自己能控制一切！","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......","id":179,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"不信的话，你搜一下她，她身上一定有录音用的机器，她这一路上跟着我们就是为了观察我们，也观察那些银色的怪物！","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......乌比卡博士，要是有脱困的方法，你该开口了。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"埃琳娜......","id":185,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"奥利维亚，我的确没有把实验信息告诉你......","id":187,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"但我绝对不会骗你。","id":188,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"桑尼，迈尔，我也没有骗过你们。","id":189,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我......真的不知道对付它们的方法。","id":191,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#8$1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我记录它们的数据，研究它们，都是因为我也想解决眼前的问题......我说过了，这是我工作的一部分。","id":193,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嗯......","id":195,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"迈尔先生，我想埃琳娜没有撒谎。","id":197,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你能把乔伊丝还给我们了吗？","id":198,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"哈......哈哈哈......","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"character","id":202},{"type":"Text","text":"拓荒者盯着白面鸮，突然抬手。","id":203},{"type":"Text","text":"一声叫喊凝在了赫默嗓子眼，无人机接收到了主人的意志，狠狠撞向拓荒者的身体。","id":204},{"type":"Text","text":"可他只是从白面鸮手上取下了一样东西。","id":205},{"type":"Text","text":"那是他在几个小时前亲手给她戴上的紧急医疗环。","id":206},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......","id":208,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我......我都干了些什么啊？","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"摩尔医生......","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"你会怪我吗？你会不会后悔曾经对我那么好？","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我这样的人......根本不配被你拯救。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"character","id":215},{"type":"Text","text":"医生回到了她的朋友们身边。她依然安静，美丽，无瑕。","id":216},{"type":"Text","text":"可是所有人都无处可逃了。这座实验室就是一个为他们提前准备好的墓穴。","id":217},{"type":"Text","text":"没有人能得救，这该死的环只是那该死的公司给他们套上的镣铐。","id":218},{"type":"Text","text":"他们都得不到自由，除非......","id":219},{"type":"Text","text":"拓荒者突然把紧急医疗环整个塞进了嘴里。","id":220},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"迈尔！","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"领、领队......","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你在干什么？快吐出来！","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#5$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这医疗环......","id":228,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"里面还剩大量止痛剂。","id":230,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"一口气吞掉这么多，心脏根本受不了，他会休克的！","id":232,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我见过......有人偷偷地把这个吞下去......","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"他们都死了！","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"那他们很......幸运。","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"该死，你给我吐出来！","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我按住他的嘴，萨姆，你给我揍他肚子！","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":242},{"type":"character","id":243},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":245},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","text":"","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":248},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","text":"","id":251},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":252},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":253},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":254},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","power":"5","times":"2","fadetime":"0.51","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"咳咳......咳咳咳！","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"再加把劲，我看到医疗环的形状了！","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"奥利维亚，我们一起帮他——","id":261,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......奥利维亚？","id":263,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......乔伊丝。","id":265,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":266},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......","id":268,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":270},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":271},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"——程序启动。","id":273,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"她醒了？！","id":275,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#5$1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"好黑啊......","id":277,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"外面......为什么这么黑？","id":279,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"黑、黑吗？可是走廊上的灯都开着啊。","id":281,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"乔伊丝，你的眼睛......是不是出问题了？","id":282,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.6","id":284,"musicid":3},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......光。","id":285,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"想要光......有光的地方......很温暖。","id":286,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"一起往前走......","id":287,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"不害怕......","id":288,"figure":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你......你能听见我们说话吗？","id":290,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她不能。","id":292,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"这是怎么回事？","id":294,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我也不知道怎么回事，但这不像乔伊丝说出来的话。","id":296,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"呃，她的病......","id":298,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我非常熟悉乔伊丝，她手术前后都不是这个语气。","id":300,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......确实。","id":302,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#3$1","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你很意外。你并不知道乔伊丝身上发生了什么。","id":304,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这说明情况早就脱离了你的控制。","id":305,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"埃琳娜，关于这项实验......你真的该开口了。","id":307,"figure":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"难道多萝西真的......","id":309,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"无论如何，我都不想看到任何人因为这个实验受伤，尤其是乔伊丝。","id":311,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"也许你是对的，我们本该一起解决这个问题......","id":312,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":313},{"type":"character","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温柔的女声","text":"没关系，埃琳娜，不必再犹豫了。","id":315,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温柔的女声","text":"是我邀请大家到这里来的，无论是赫默医生还是我的拓荒者朋友们，大家都有权知道真相。","id":316,"figure":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你一直在......监控我们？","id":318,"figure":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1"},